爱尔兰音乐传奇人物西尼德·奥康纳 (Sinead O'Connor) 去世，享年 56 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-ged-56-3473863?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies- 56岁Anagricel DuranWed, 26 Jul 2023 18:15:02 +0000 Music NewsNews..Pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3473863 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2020 年 2 月 9 日，西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor) 在洛杉矶埃尔雷剧院 (El Rey Theater)。图片来源：Lindsey Best for the Washington Post/GETTY" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手因翻唱 Prince 的《Nothing Compares 2 U》而享誉全球</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">爱尔兰音乐传奇人物西尼德·奥康纳 (Sinead O&#39;Connor) 去世，享年 56 岁</a><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2020 年 2 月 9 日，西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor) 在洛杉矶埃尔雷剧院 (El Rey Theater)。图片来源：Lindsey Best for the Washington Post/GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据《 <a href="https://www.irishtimes.com/culture/music/2023/07/26/sinead-oconnor-acclaimed-dublin-singer-dies-aged-56/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>爱尔兰时报》</em></a>报道，著名爱尔兰歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">西妮德·奥康纳</a>去世，享年 56 岁。</p><p> 1966 年 12 月 8 日，她出生于都柏林，原名西妮德·玛丽·伯纳黛特·奥康纳 (Sinéad Marie Bernadette O&#39;Connor)，她在 80 年代末凭借首张专辑《The Lion And The Cobra》而声名鹊起。</p><p>在她的整个职业生涯中，奥康纳发行了 10 张录音室专辑，其中她翻唱的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">Prince</a>的《Nothing Compares 2 U》获得了全世界的赞誉，并于 1990 年被<em>Billboard</em>评为世界第一单曲。</p><p>死因尚未公布。 </p><figure id="attachment_3473869" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3473869" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3473869" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage.jpg" alt="西妮德·奥康纳。图片来源：SGranitz/GETTY" width="2000" height="1368" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage-218x150.jpg 218w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage-400x274.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage-800x547.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage-696x476.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage-1392x952.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-OConnor-Photo-by-SGranitz_WireImage-1068x731.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3473869" class="wp-caption-text">西妮德·奥康纳。图片来源：SGranitz/GETTY</figcaption></figure><p>她去世的消息传出一年前，她 17 岁的儿子谢恩 (Shane) 于 2022 年 1 月在自杀监视中逃离医院后结束了自己的生命。她最后的社交媒体帖子是一条推文，上面贴着她已故儿子的照片，标题是：“从那时起，我就一直像不死的夜间生物一样生活。他是我一生的挚爱，我灵魂的灯。”</p><p>奥康纳身后留下了三个孩子杰克·雷诺兹、罗伊辛·沃特斯和耶舒亚·博纳迪奥。</p><p>这是一个突发新闻故事。请回来查看更新。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">爱尔兰音乐传奇人物西尼德·奥康纳 (Sinead O&#39;Connor) 去世，享年 56 岁</a><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ;
